version_description: Very simple song to play on either acoustic guitar,or electric with a little bit of chorus,no capo is required.I have included all links and the you tube link.
Complete chords and lyrics / capo 3rd fret (easier to play) / suggestions for chord voicings.
Includes tablature for the main riffs, backing vocals, and a chord legend.
Neat accurate formatting, chord legend included.
Well-aligned and complete chords for all parts of the song / intermediate version featuring suspended chords and suggestions for playable voicings / tab for intro guitar.
